## table attribute_def | doc="An attribute definition (title, assignee, …). value_type is one of text|number|bool|card_ref|card_ref[]. For card_ref / card_ref[] value_types target_card_type_id names the card_type whose cards are the valid values — that is what unifies every pick-from-a-list attribute (assignee / milestone / component / tag plus any custom card_type a project admin defines): each is a card_ref to value-cards of a specific card_type. There is no enum table and no privileged workflow attribute baked into the schema."

### meta
name_column
name

